TOKEN_CHANGE

Fields
Field Name Description
componentsRemoved - [COMPONENT!] A list of components removed based on the changed state
componentsAdded - [COMPONENT!] A list of components added based on the changed state
errorMessages - [String] A list of error messages related to the changed state. If the change was successful this field returns null
state - STATE Represents the changed state
pricingDetails - PRICING_DETAILS Holds pricing details for the changed state.
configuration - DATA Holds the complete configuration scope, equal to what you get with tokenConfigurationQuery
configurationDetails - CONFIGURATION_DETAILS_QUERY Holds the complete configuration summary scope, equal to what you get with tokenConfigurationDetailsQuery
stateFromInput - STATE Holds the state generated directly from the input
Example
{
  "componentsRemoved": [COMPONENT],
  "componentsAdded": [COMPONENT],
  "errorMessages": ["xyz789"],
  "state": STATE,
  "pricingDetails": PRICING_DETAILS,
  "configuration": DATA,
  "configurationDetails": CONFIGURATION_DETAILS_QUERY,
  "stateFromInput": STATE
}

Types

UPH

Fields
Field Name Description
name - String Code of the component
language - String This field is not used
structureWeek - Int Structure week start of the component
pno34Plus - String Pno34 Plus that contains Market, model year and Pno34 including standard wheel/ selected wheel option, accessories, packs For more details about Pno34Plus, please refer this link : [URL] https://intranet.volvocars.net/sites/CCH/SitePages/PNO34+.aspx
modelYear - Int Model year of configuration
marketingCode - Int Marketing code
type - String Type of component - for example COL for color
price - Float Price of the component
relativePrice - Float Relative price of the component (diff calculated based on current selection)
text - String This field is not used
pno12 - String This field is not used
available - Boolean To hold the available state. True when component is available to select, false otherwise
selected - Boolean To hold the selected state. True when component is selected in configuration already
included - Boolean To hold the included state. True when component is auto-selected due to must rule or component is part of pack etc
required - [DEPENDENT!] Must included component (must rule) will be listed here
requiredExclusively - [DEPENDENT!] To hold the must rule with exchangeable components
group - String This field is not used
category - String Category of the component which is received from SCNG
categorization - CATEGORIZATION Categorization of the component which is received from SCNG
tags - [String!] Tags is defined in SCNG for the component
description - String Long Description of the component
displayName - String Short description of the component
displayType - UPH_DISPLAY_TYPE Display type of the component
usp - [String!] This field is not used
image - String Image url of the component in view-1
image1 - String Image url of the component in view-2
image2 - String Image url of the component in view-3
video1 - String Video url of the component
video2 - String Video url of the component
requiredChanges - [REQUIRED_CHANGES!] The list of changes required when user selects/ deselects the respective component This also has list of the other components added/ removed upon selection of the component Token is given for selection/ deselection
visible - Boolean This defines whether the component is visible or not
missingPrice - Boolean
componentTypeId - String ComponentTypeId holds CPAM component type. For example : Engine - 4, SV- 5 etc
pricing - [PRICING] This hold price information of the component For more details about pricing strategy, please refer this link : [URL] https://intranet.volvocars.net/sites/CCH/SitePages/Pricing---strategy-to-implementation.aspx
classification - CLASSIFICATION This gives classification (Group/ sub-group) of the component
sort - Int This gives sort order
userSelected - Boolean User selected status. True when the component is user selected
componentPrice - PRICE_DATA This gives component price
forcedBy - FORCED_BY When a component gets included forcefully by package selection, the package code and short diplay name will be shown in this field
partOf - [PART_OF] If this component is part of a another component, such as a package
co2Effect - Boolean Co2 effect of component. This comes only for accessoires currently
optionType - String Option type holds type of option. A-Accessory, L-Local Option, F-Factory Options
casVisualized - Boolean Feature is visualized in CAS
default - Boolean true if the value is in the startingPoint of the car.
_energyEfficiency - String
_state - String
_priceConfigInput - String
_locale - String
hex - String
materials - [MATERIAL!]
features - [FEATURE!]
content - UpholsteryContent
Arguments
locale - String

Defaults to the query locale

market - String

Defaults to market part of locale

preview - Boolean

Fetch working copy instead of published
globalName - String
globalShortName - String
Example
{
  "name": "xyz789",
  "language": "xyz789",
  "structureWeek": 987,
  "pno34Plus": "abc123",
